can exhume the bodies.

184
00:14:56.930 --> 00:14:58.665
move them. cremate them...

185
00:14:58.765 --> 00:15:00.300
whatever they choose.

186
00:15:01.101 --> 00:15:02.435
Well. what if you...

187
00:15:03.203 --> 00:15:05.438
