Remember?

242
00:17:40.593 --> 00:17:41.928
Everybody Poops.

243
00:17:42.795 --> 00:17:44.397
Children's book.

244
00:17:44.497 --> 00:17:47.234
It normalizes. you know.
basic human behavior.

245
00:17:47.334 --> 00:17:49.068
body functions.
Wh...

246
